NAME
  VTK::IOExtra
LIBRARY_NAME
  vtkIOExtra
DESCRIPTION
  Heavy / third-party data file readers and writers (Exodus, FLUENT CFF, SEG-Y).
  Split out of the VTK::IO kit so the core native-format readers (XML, Legacy,
  PLY, Image) consolidate into libvtkIO on their own, leaving this kit to carry
  the heavyweight data-IO formats. This lets a packaging tier ship the core IO
  readers without the heavy ones.
